					Will You Have EnoughOrange Money® for Retirement?				




Tool
			






 





Grow and protect your retirement savings with the Voya Journey Index Annuity, an innovative fixed index annuity that offers full participation in the growth, if any, in one or more dynamic indices over a seven year period.




Key Features

Your annuity value will not go down
Tax deferred growth—you don’t pay income tax until you take a withdrawal
Credited interest rate linked to multiple index strategies
Fixed rate strategy provides a guaranteed interest credited rate
No early withdrawal penalties after the seventh year
Issued by Voya Insurance and Annuity Company
 

Suitable For




You are near or in retirement and  looking for a safe place to invest a portion of their retirement savings
You are looking for protection from market downturns and more growth potential than typically offered by  bank CDs
You are comfortable leaving this money invested in this product for seven years 







Eligibility

Issue Ages0-80 owner and annuitant
 Premium$15,000 minimum initial premium (subject to change without notice)
No minimum premium per strategy 
$1.5 million maximum premium without prior home office approval
 AvailabilityNot available in all states
 

